---------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------
Stonebreaker
---------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------
NOTE: These formulas use global_attack_mod to store static modifiers.  
    -You must have at least one mod selected or the macro breaks.  Create a Placeholder with a value of 0 to make sure macros work. 
    -Placing a space after the damage will make the formula easier to view. For example, rage should look like "2 "

NOTE:These formulas use global_damage_mods to store additional dice.  
    -You don't have to keep any global dice mods checked.  Macros will work either way.
    -Placing a space after the damage will make the formula easier to view.  
    -To prevent red/green make sure to do a critical fail 1 less than dice minimum and critical success 1 higher than dice maximum.  For example, bless should look like what's in quotes "1d8cf<0cs>100 ".
---------------------------------------------


---------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------
Stonebreaker-1H with Magic Weapon (Default +1, adjust macros as needed above +1)
---------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------
Stonebreaker-1H with Magic Weapon - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
Stonebreaker-1H-Str-MW-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Str-MW-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Str-MW-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Str-MW-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Str-MW-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Str-MW-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Str-MW-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Str-MW-Disadvantage3-Nested}}
---------------------------------------------
Stonebreaker-1H-Str-MW-Standard-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee - Stonebreaker-1H&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Stonebreaker-1H attack*&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[1d10!cf<1cs>10 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[1 [Magic Weapon]]] [Magic Weapon] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Bludgeoning&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] + $[[4]] Bludgeoning + $[[5]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Stonebreaker=On a hit Stonebreaker deals an additional [[1d10]] to objects, constructs, or creatures made of stone &#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
Stonebreaker-1H-Str-MW-Advantage-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee - Stonebreaker-1H (Advantage)&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Stonebreaker-1H attack at **Advantage** *&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[2d10!!cf<1cs>10kh1 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[1 [Magic Weapon]]] [Magic Weapon] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Bludgeoning&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] + $[[4]] Bludgeoning + $[[5]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Stonebreaker=On a hit Stonebreaker deals an additional [[1d10]] to objects, constructs, or creatures made of stone &#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
Stonebreaker-1H-Str-MW-Disadvantage-Nested
