---------------------------------------------
Stonebreaker-1H with Magic Weapon and Crusher Feat (Default +1, adjust macros as needed above +1)
---------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------
Stonebreaker-1H with Magic Weapon and Crusher Feat - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
Stonebreaker-1H-Crusher-Str-MW-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Crusher-Str-MW-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Crusher-Str-MW-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Crusher-Str-MW-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Crusher-Str-MW-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Crusher-Str-MW-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Crusher-Str-MW-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|Stonebreaker-1H-Crusher-Str-MW-Disadvantage3-Nested}}
---------------------------------------------
Stonebreaker-1H-Crusher-Str-MW-Standard-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee - Stonebreaker-1H&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Stonebreaker-1H attack*&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[1d10!cf<1cs>10 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[1 [Magic Weapon]]] [Magic Weapon] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Bludgeoning&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] + $[[4]] Bludgeoning + $[[5]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Stonebreaker=On a hit Stonebreaker deals an additional [[1d10]] to objects, constructs, or creatures made of stone &#125;&#125; {{Crusher Hit= Once per turn, when you hit a creature with an attack that deals bludgeoning damage, you can move it 5 feet to an unoccupied space, provided the target is no more than one size larger than you.&#125;&#125; {{Crusher Crit= When you score a critical hit that deals bludgeoning damage to a creature, attack rolls against that creature are made with advantage until the start of your next turn.&#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
