&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee - Stonebreaker-1H (Disadvantage x3)&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Stonebreaker-1H attack at **Triple Disadvantage** *&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[4d10!!cf<1cs>10kl1 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[1 [Magic Weapon]]] [Magic Weapon] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Bludgeoning&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] + $[[4]] Bludgeoning + $[[5]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Stonebreaker=On a hit Stonebreaker deals an additional [[1d10]] to objects, constructs, or creatures made of stone &#125;&#125; {{Crusher Hit= Once per turn, when you hit a creature with an attack that deals bludgeoning damage, you can move it 5 feet to an unoccupied space, provided the target is no more than one size larger than you.&#125;&#125; {{Crusher Crit= When you score a critical hit that deals bludgeoning damage to a creature, attack rolls against that creature are made with advantage until the start of your next turn.&#125;&#125;
