&{template:default} {{name=Melee - Stonebreaker-1H}} {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes an Offhand Stonebreaker-1H attack*}} [[ [[ [[1d10!cf<1cs>10 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[1 [Magic Weapon]]] [Magic Weapon] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Bludgeoning}} {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies}} {{Static=$[[3]] Bludgeoning + $[[4]] Varies}} {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** }} {{Static Total=$[[6]] ***Static Damage*** }} {{Total=$[[7]] **Total Damage** }} {{Stonebreaker=On a hit Stonebreaker deals an additional [[1d10]] to objects, constructs, or creatures made of stone.}} {{Crusher Hit= Once per turn, when you hit a creature with an attack that deals bludgeoning damage, you can move it 5 feet to an unoccupied space, provided the target is no more than one size larger than you.}} {{Crusher Crit= When you score a critical hit that deals bludgeoning damage to a creature, attack rolls against that creature are made with advantage until the start of your next turn.}} 
